data.title: This Robotic Surgery Legend Is Pouring $100 Million Into Next-Gen Medical Startups
data.description: Fred Moll, the cofounder of $200 billion Intuitive Surgical, has invested in some 15 companies building robots that could help make both complex and common surgeries more accessible to everyone.
data.author: Amy Feldman
data.keywords: fred moll,intuitive surgical,surgical robots,robotics,medtech,dr. moll,sonder capital,telesurgery,SS Innovations,XCath
